---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Gisenyi (Rubavu) - Lake Kivu's Beach Paradise">
  <Header />
  
  <div style="padding-top: 120px;" class="s">
    <div class="s-narrow" style="margin: 0 auto;">
      <span class="s-label">Lake Kivu</span>
      <h1 class="s-heading">Gisenyi<br><em>Rwanda's Lakeside Escape</em></h1>
      <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <img src="/images/rwanda_landscape_hero_1763982560164.png" alt="Lake Kivu at golden hour" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;">
      </div>
      <div class="s-body" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <p>Gisenyi (also known as Rubavu) is Rwanda's premier beach destination on the shores of Lake Kivu. With its white-sand beaches, colonial-era architecture, and stunning sunsets, this lakeside town offers the perfect relaxation after gorilla trekking.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Top Activities</h3>
        <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; list-style-position: inside;">
          <li>🏖️ Beach Relaxation — swim in Africa's sixth-largest lake</li>
          <li>🚤 Boat Cruises — sunset tours to nearby islands</li>
          <li>🚣 Kayaking & Paddleboarding — explore the calm waters</li>
          <li>🎣 Fishing Trips — catch fresh tilapia with local fishermen</li>
          <li>🏨 Colonial Hotel Rwanda — historic lakeside accommodation</li>
          <li>☕ Coffee Plantation Tours — visit nearby farms</li>
          <li>🌅 Sunset Drinks — at La Corniche beachfront promenade</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Local Cuisine</h3>
        <p>Don't miss fresh tilapia from Lake Kivu, grilled to perfection and served with plantains and sambaza (small fried fish). The lakeside restaurants offer spectacular views of the Congo's Virunga Mountains across the water.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box" style="background: var(--bg2); padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);">
          <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Travel Tip</h4>
          <p>Gisenyi is just a 3-hour drive from Kigali or 1.5 hours from Musanze. Consider spending 2-3 nights here to fully unwind after gorilla trekking. Many luxury lodges offer direct beach access and spa facilities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>